{"tid":1406063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係m記聽見兩個小學雞係度吹水","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:06:26.000Z","uid":107262,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc9085b4ae99e4c04a47d2788dfe527c8a188d7","tid":1406063,"uid":107262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"發完夢訓醒翻屋企m記食野 見到兩個小學雞係度打傳說對決<br />\n<br />\n小學雞A：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小學雞B：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點解政府講左唔推行反送中 佢地都繼續遊行既 （我唸佢係想講送中條例）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：因為政府唔肯講＂撤回＂兩隻字lo～得哩兩隻字有法律效力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦～～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你 咪撚再死得唔得呀！<br />\n<br />\n個小朋友玩得好唔好我唔知，但係一個6 7歲既小朋友講到哩d野，我係下一代，下下一代身上睇到希望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日大家加油！"}]}